quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,‘Oh ban geupeugah aneuk Mariyam Jeut keu teuladan kuasa Allah Kawom gata dum ka jeut keu karu
  43,58,Jikheun dum laju teuma jipeugah Tuhan geutanyoe dum got nibak nyan Meukeusud jihnyan sit keu jibantah Bandum jih sit nyan kawom bantahan
  43,59,Kon laen gopnyan cit hamba Allah Kamoe bri nikmat teuma keu gopnyan Jeut keu misalan nyang jroh sileupah Jeut keu ibarat Bani israil
  43,60,Gata pih Neubri ban nyang hʻeut Allah Meu Kamoe kheundak keugata meuhat Ngon malaikat meugantoe bagah Meugantoe gata ngon malaikat Di bumoe meuhat jeut keu khaliphah
  43,61,Jeut keu ‘eleumee teuntang kiamat Gata dum meuhat bek chok sileupah Taikot treuk lon nyoe jalan teupat
  43,62,Chetan nyang laknat bek ek jiteugah Keubit roe chetan musoh nyata that Gata bak sisat jiyue meulangkah
  43,63,‘Oh ban troh Isa geuba ngon ayat Lon ba hikeumah teuma geupeugah Lom lon jak peutrang keunoe bak gata Nyang tameudawa mangat bek salah Teuma takwa gata keu Tuhan Tataʻat keu lon Neuyue le Allah
  43,64,Allah Tuhanlon ngon Tuhan gata Droeneuhnyan saja nyang beu taseumah Jalan nyoe keuh nyang jalan nyang teupat
  43,65,Han jitem pakat teuma jibantah Jipeudong dawa sabe keudroe jih Ceulaka treuk jih nyang lalem leupah Keu jihnyan azeub uroe kiamat Uroe peudeh that hanaban peugah
  43,66,Peue laen jipren meu kon Kiamat Hana jan siat cit troh le bagah Hana meujithee ka troh kiamat
  43,67,Ngon rakan jih that musoh sileupah Meumusoh-musoh sabe keudroe-droe Meu kon ureueng nyoe takwa keu Allah
  43,68,Ho ka dum gata hamba-hamba Lon Uroenyoe bandum gata ka leupah Hana peue takot hana susah le
  43,69,Iman lam ate keu ayat Allah Soe nyang meuiman keu ayat Kamoe Lom pih bak Kamoe droejih meunyerah
  43,70,Jak tamong laju ngon judo gata Dalam churuga seunang that leupah Bandum teuh seunang dalam churuga
  43,71,Keunan troh geuba pingan deungon glah Pingan meuh ngon glah ka na soe idang Bandum ureueng nyan ladat sileupah Peue napsu ate ladat di mata Bandum seudia han ek tapeugah Lom bandum gata keukai di sinan
  43,72,Pusaka teuh nyan churuga indah c Keu gata bandum geubri pusaka Balah usaha masa nyang sudah
  43,73,Boh kayee le that sinan keu gata Tapajoh sigra ladat that leupah
  43,74,Awak nyang salah keukai lam azeub Keu jihnyan teumpat nuraka juah
  43,75,Putoh asa bit di jih lam azeub Hana meusiat pih jih geupeuglah
  43,76,Teuma kon Kamoe nyang elanya jih Tapi keudroe jih lalem that leupah
  43,77,Jikheun hai Malek han ek meutheun le Tayue poh mate kamoe bak Allah Geujaweub di kah teutap lagee nyan
  43,78,Kon ka watee nyan dum Kamoe peugah c Haba nyang beuna meuba bak gata Tapi dum gata beunci teuh leupah Beunci that gata keupeue nyang beuna
  43,79,Jipakat teuma lom bak buet salah Jipakat dum jih saboh rencana Kamoe rencana leubeh lom ceudah
  43,80,Hana meudeunge rahsia jihnyan jisangka meunan kaphe seurakah Nyang jimeus‘ah-s‘ah jipeugot pakat Bandum geusurat hana meuilah Bandum geutuleh le Rasul Kamoe Nyang jih pubuet nyoe beuna ngon salah
  43,81,Takheun meunyoe bit na aneuk Tuhan Lon keuh ureueng phon keunan lon seumah
  43,82,Maha suci that Po langet bumoe Po ‘arasy lom nyoe ban nyang jih peugah
  43,83,Bah jilop keunan jimaen-maen ‘Oh troh uroenyan meunyesai teulah Akan meureumpok jih ngon uroenyan Ka janji Tuhan dilee Neupeugah
  43,84,Sideh di langet Droeneuh nyan Tuhan Di bumoe meunan hana meuubah That bijaksana dumpeue Neuteupue Hana meusapeue pih na meuilah
  43,85,Maha suci that Tuhanku sidroe Langet ngon bumoe sit milek Allah Keurajeun langet keurajeun bumoe Bandum ngon asoe Droeneuh peurintah Pajan kiamat Droeneuh nyang teupue Bandum gata nyoe tawoe bak Allah
  43,86,Nyang jikheun Tuhan dum le awaknyan Chuphevuʻat pih tan keu jih Neukeubah Han jeut chupheuʻat bandum awaknyan Nyang jikheun Tuhan nyang bukon Allah Meulengkan ureueng nyang saksi beuna Geupubuet teuma bandum peurintah Nyang jeut keu saksi bak keubenaran ‘Eleumee gopnyan Neubri le Allah
  43,87,Meunyo tatanyong ubak awaknyan Soe peujeut jihnyan sit jikheun Allah Pakon sit di jih ek jipeupaleng
  43,88,Geukheun ya Tuhan nyang Maha Murah Kawomnyoe bandum han jimeuiman
  43,89,Bah keu jih meunan bek that tapapah Takheun seulamat mantong keu jih nyoe Jiteupue dudoe akibat salah
  44,1,Hamim Tuhan nyang teupue meukeusud ayat Sabab Hadharat hana Neupeugah
  44,2,Demi Kitab nyoe keubit nyata that
  44,3,Malam beureukat hanaban peugah Kamoe peutron bak malam beureukat Kamoe peuingat dum hamba Allah
  44,4,Dalam kitab nyoe le that hikeumah Uleh Hadharat Neutrang Neupeugah
  44,5,Bandum urusan asai bak Kamoe Meukirem keunoe geuba risalah
  44,6,Atranyan rahmat nibak Po gata Allah Taʻala kuasa leupah Dumpeue Neudeunge dumpeue Neuteupue
  44,7,Po langet bumoe deungon blah bicah Langet ngon bumoe ngon bandum asoe Meunyo gata nyoe yakin keu Allah
  44,8,Udep ngon mate lam jaroe Tuhan Tan laen Tuhan meulengkan Allah Po gata bandum ngon yah-yah gata Nyang dilee masa ka abeh sudah
  44,9,Tapi jih lam chok bandum jimaen
  44,10,Tapreh troh angen asap trang leupah Sideh di langet asap geukirem
  44,11,Bak bandum insan nyang pubuet salah Azeub peudeh that asap nyoe lagoe
  44,12,Wahe Po kamoe Neubri meusiblah Neupeuglah kamoe nibak azeub nyoe Meuiman kamoe jinoe le bagah
  44,13,Pakri roe di jih hana jiingat Rasul nyata that ka troh geulangkah Geujakba bak jih haba peuingat
  44,14,Jipaleng ligat jikheun beurakah Jikheun jihnyan na ureueng peureunoe Gila that jihnyoe nyan jijak peugah
  44,15,Kamoe peukureueng azeub nyan bacut Lom cit tapubuet lagee nyang sudah
  44,16,Saboh pukulan nyang raya that-that Uroenyan meuhat Kamoe jok balah